{"tid":1304434,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"革命不是請客吃飯，不是做文章，不是繪畫繡花，不能那樣雅致，那樣從容不迫，文質彬彬，那樣溫良恭儉讓。","createTime":"2019-07-10T15:14:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T15:42:49.000Z","uid":37811,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b961fa05f1e03746be3d796ccfeb804c44f31b78","tid":1304434,"uid":37811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:14:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">革命不是請客吃飯，不是做文章，不是繪畫繡花，不能那樣雅致，那樣從容不迫，文質彬彬，那樣溫良恭儉讓。</span></span>革命是暴動，是一個階級推翻一個階級的暴烈的行動<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日有幾撚多人因為focus 係個連儂牆度呀？<br />\n<br />\n我前幾日已經開post 講過一次<br />\n<br />\n叫連登仔focus 返係唔同嘅訴求<br />\n<br />\n過咗幾日 <br />\n77過咗 林鄭壽終正寢咗 訴求唔同咗唔緊要<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有人話林鄭講壽終正寢就等於完咗<br />\n<br />\n再追求落字眼上光執著係無意義<br />\n<br />\n應該要重返問題嘅重心<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">實行雙普選</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果有人唔同意壽終正寢等於完咗嘅唔緊要<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我自己都覺得未應該完</span></span><br />\n<br />\n咁就再討論 再行動令到政府回應<br />\n<br />\n但係你班連登仔呢幾日 日日唔係打寶礦力飛機<br />\n<br />\n就係係度J連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n我想問吓呢2個動作對於目前形勢有咩幫助？<br />\n<br />\n玩連儂牆嘅目的係比同路人keep住團火<br />\n<br />\n團火係要拎出黎用係主要行動上面架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家行動已經到咗樽頸位<br />\n<br />\n點解唔花多啲心思落去行動上面？<br />\n<br />\n咁多位連登仔<br />\n<br />\n我希望你地記住毛魔嘅金句<br />\n<br />\n革命不是請客吃飯，不是做文章，不是繪畫繡花，不能那樣雅致，那樣從容不迫，文質彬彬，那樣溫良恭儉讓。<br />\n<br />\n連儂牆同做文章，繪畫繡花無分別<br />\n<br />\n我求吓你地咪再將你地100%嘅精力放係連儂牆同寶礦力身上面<br />\n<br />\n好唔好？"},{"pid":"bbf259b8aadeed490a01de0396a0c744c784635f","tid":1304434,"uid":37811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:15:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7de5891ce0bfb0bb8d6edab54e7bc5f6ce8a1d1d","tid":1304434,"uid":37811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:15:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9387d3fe3b5611fb4be5c87aa8fe4668056f3045","tid":1304434,"uid":37811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:16:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5e2ebf0ea674fe4e78fdfd7c0e5ce06a4dc783d","tid":1304434,"uid":37811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:16:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ca65e6435d87b7a42d9d54663729998e1f1ab61","tid":1304434,"uid":37811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:16:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3793c379e90b48246d61ae25a72440a9ddc0f24","tid":1304434,"uid":37811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:16:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"857b83810477bbfe896dee90f458d18befb7207f","tid":1304434,"uid":37811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:17:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b8f48f9a62a0ae40e7d2ca0fd4fb4b1672fc57c","tid":1304434,"uid":37811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:17:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aecb51ca64a3b5d38d4bc13d315558976db86325","tid":1304434,"uid":37811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:17:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"57d2b386718becde65a3b4afce46471ababc1c6d","tid":1304434,"uid":37811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:17:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e4cd71af18037b44d72e243129053ff80260b04a","tid":1304434,"uid":37811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:18:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d137bc90e7acda1a3da6d821c92f08ea4f7c69f1","tid":1304434,"uid":37811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:18:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70948c3413b31954ed3d86e675fcaeab5ceda74a","tid":1304434,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:18:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5df04f2fc5ed2d26781bff5f804ed5764175a526","tid":1304434,"uid":37811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:19:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"035c967da65eb85bf2fea22a4205c2c258946356","tid":1304434,"uid":37811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:20:08.000Z","msg":"呢啲你呀媽係女人嘅道理永遠就係個個都知<br />\n但係一到行事起黎永遠個個都唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e38dbe46afcf307b619353dd3aa67615549d0406","tid":1304434,"uid":37811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:20:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe99ab522e786acfe5b67b04440b227f9fc63266","tid":1304434,"uid":37811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:20:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df16e48b577e3f2770a77df4a55e61098ff27ee9","tid":1304434,"uid":37811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:21:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"837e4763bc8246385ffd0c410586a576eb0b6f44","tid":1304434,"uid":37811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:21:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cecb053e5a38263fd1bf459cdff886fee9a972c3","tid":1304434,"uid":37811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:21:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a42ac9573a02cd10287dd01d52c88adeada47f1","tid":1304434,"uid":37811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:21:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5df3f23d033a595b740c45cf76bdfd475a50fbb1","tid":1304434,"uid":44870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:21:38.000Z","msg":"重申抗爭所堅持之五大訴求:<br />\n一、撤回修例<br />\n二、撤回6.12暴動定性<br />\n三、撤銷反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、責成獨立調查委員會追究警方濫權<br />\n五、實行雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求從未得到任何回應.<br />\n香港人一齊聚焦返我地嘅初心,可以嗎?"},{"pid":"a5555fe85a9b3373a3ccf3835b60363d285499d0","tid":1304434,"uid":37811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:21:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"360148f3ec21041355039658937b889d78391ce0","tid":1304434,"uid":3